title: Super Duper Music Collection
description:
I present to you my collection of anime music.

516 dongs - 39 hours of listening

Genres in descending order:
Anime, Jrock, Electro, Trance, Jpop, dubstep, other.

ALL dongs have high quality album art aswell as detailed and accurate info.
i'm a nerd like that, it has to look nice :)

The collection is a not a "top 500" or "best of" sort of collection, but instead my personal and subjective tastes.
It's mostly year 2000+ music with a few 19's mixed in, infact there is only 13 dongs from before year 2000.

I hope you'll enjoy it as much as i do.
